Class HadoopCompat

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.hadoop.tools.util.HadoopCompat

public class HadoopCompat
extends Object

Utility methods to allow applications to deal with inconsistencies between MapReduce Context Objects API between Hadoop 1.x and 2.x.
